OL,5,Crule
OL,7,FPrivate parking companies have pledged
OL,8,Fto update their code of conduct after
OL,9,Flegal action was launched against a
OL,10,Fdriver for taking more than five
OL,11,Fminutes to pay for using a car park.
OL,13,FTwo industry bodies representing the
OL,14,Fsector announced they have established
OL,15,Fa panel to revise the code to ensure
OL,16,Fit "protects genuine motorists who
OL,17,Fhave difficulty making prompt payment
OL,18,Fon entry".
