OL,7,FThe British Parking Association (BPA)
OL,8,Fand the International Parking
OL,9,FCommunity (IPC) said the panel will
OL,10,Falso "fast-track updates to the code
OL,11,Fto reflect technological advancements".
OL,13,FPrivate parking businesses have been
OL,14,Faccused of using misleading and
OL,15,Fconfusing signs, aggressive debt
OL,16,Fcollection and unreasonable fees.
OL,18,FIt emerged in November that drivers in
OL,19,FBritain are being hit by an average of
OL,20,Fmore than 41,000 parking tickets a day
OL,21,Fby private companies.
