OL,7,FSome 3.8 million tickets were handed
OL,8,Fout between July and September 2024,
OL,9,Faccording to analysis of government
OL,10,Fdata by the PA news agency and
OL,11,Fmotoring research charity the RAC
OL,12,FFoundation.
OL,14,FEach ticket can be up to #100, meaning
OL,15,Fthe total cost to drivers may be near
OL,16,F#4.1 million per day.
