OL,4,Ccode of conduct to address five-minute
OL,5,Crule
OL,7,FIn November last year, the BBC
OL,8,Freported that Rosey Hudson was being
OL,9,Ftaken to court by a private parking
OL,10,Fcompany for #1,906 after she
OL,11,Frepeatedly took more than five minutes
OL,12,Fto pay after entering a car park in
OL,13,FDerby because of poor mobile phone
OL,14,Fsignal.
OL,16,FA Bill to enable the introduction of a
OL,17,Fgovernment-backed code of practice for
OL,18,Fprivate parking companies received
OL,19,Froyal assent under the Conservative
OL,20,Fgovernment in March 2019.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
