OL,3,CPrivate parking companies to update
OL,4,Ccode of conduct to address five-minute
OL,5,Crule
OL,7,FIt was withdrawn in June 2022 after a
OL,8,Flegal challenge by parking companies.
OL,10,FThis code included halving the cap on
OL,11,Ftickets for most parking offences to
OL,12,F#50, creating a fairer appeals system,
OL,13,Fand banning the use of aggressive
OL,14,Flanguage on tickets.
OL,16,FIn June, the BPA and IPC published
OL,17,Ftheir own code of practice, which will
OL,18,Fbe overseen by the new panel.
