OL,7,FIPC chief executive Will Hurley said:
OL,8,F"The creation of the panel shows the
OL,9,Fcommitment the industry has to
OL,10,Fimproving the reputation of our sector.
OL,12,F"We must not forget the valuable
OL,13,Fservice we provide to ensure the vast
OL,14,Fmajority of people can park when and
OL,15,Fwhere they need to."
OL,17,FBPA chief executive Andrew Pester
OL,18,Fsaid: "We want to demonstrate that not
OL,19,Fonly are we serious about raising
OL,20,Fstandards but also making decisive
OL,21,Fchanges to the code when issues arise."
