OL,7,FIn relation to the five-minute rule,
OL,8,Fthe organisations stressed that "many
OL,9,Fcar parks ... are pay on entry", and
OL,10,Fit is important drivers "read signage
OL,11,Fand follow instructions".
OL,13,FRAC senior policy officer Rod Dennis
OL,14,Fsaid: "The fact that the private
OL,15,Fparking industry is already having to
OL,16,Freview its own code, just months after
OL,17,Fit was introduced, shows it's not
OL,18,Fworking in drivers' interests.
