OL,7,F"This is yet another reason why the
OL,8,Flaunch of the long-overdue official
OL,9,FPrivate Parking Code of Practice, that
OL,10,Fbecame law five years ago, is very
OL,11,Fmuch needed.
OL,13,F"We fear that without this, drivers
OL,14,Fwho use private car parks will
OL,15,Fcontinue to be worse off."
